org.apache.mina.common
Class TrafficMask

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.mina.common.TrafficMask

public class TrafficMask
extends Object

A type-safe mask that is used to control the traffic of IoSession with IoSession.setTrafficMask(TrafficMask).

Version:
$Rev: 451854 $, $Date: 2006-10-02 11:30:11 +0900 (월, 02 10월 2006) $
